flowchart TD
  A[Offer and request are matched] --> B[Create JOATU agreement in pending state]
  B --> C[Agreement show page displays details and participants]
  C --> D{Participant decision}
  D -- Accept --> E[Accept action]
  E --> F[Agreement status becomes accepted]
  F --> G[Offer and request close]
  F --> H[Decision timestamp and participant roles remain visible]
  D -- Reject --> I[Reject action]
  I --> J[Agreement status becomes rejected]
  J --> K[Show rejected state to participants]
